# Force binary handling for asset/binary file types so NO checkout, merge, or
# platform (esp. Windows) ever applies line-ending / text normalization to them.
#
# History: the www-new image tree was once committed through a tool that treated
# these GIFs as text and mangled the bytes (908 of them failed to decode). They
# were repaired from the original `archspace.tar.gz` www tier; these rules keep
# it from happening again.
*.gif   binary
*.png   binary
*.jpg   binary
*.jpeg  binary
*.ico   binary
*.bmp   binary
*.gz    binary
*.tgz   binary
*.zip   binary
*.jar   binary
*.class binary
*.swf   binary
*.ttf   binary
*.woff  binary
*.woff2 binary
*.eot   binary
*.mp3   binary
*.wav   binary
*.ogg   binary
